e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"愛"},{"pid":"5267a862e1b9054b57e1b20db188a1f1870e1c9e","tid":1385531,"uid":262674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:26:23.000Z","msg":"老豆中藍睇左二十年蘋果<br />\n平安時代有叫佢幾次轉睇中立啲佢話睇慣左係都唔轉<br />\n<br />\n今日佢睇完新聞<br />\n屌完啲後生就話要轉睇東方<br />\n話佢地阻人搵食係錯<br />\n蘋果煽動人都係錯<br />\n<br />\n只能勸大家真係要小心啲<br />\n<br />\n民意唔係真實力<br />\n但係軟實力黎<br />\n無左就好難返黎"},{"pid":"98160ed73de2c05d95011320de56b80976f5e8a3","tid":1385531,"uid":290754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:27:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4de00ccae9a9c24c68e59065b5f132a6a61c5d94","tid":1385531,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:28:11.000Z","msg":"有冇多點論調可以用來安撫果班搵食大晒<br />\n話自己會遲到果班人"},{"pid":"92fde3a63f8d2ea3f2e810ff04774f112eb176ea","tid":1385531,"uid":57737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4de00ccae9a9c24c68e59065b5f132a6a61c5d94","tid":1385531,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:28:11.000Z","msg":"有冇多點論調可以用來安撫果班搵食大晒<br />\n話自己會遲到果班人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"目光放遠啲<br />\n如果放任中央蠶食香港<br />\n國際唔再相信一國兩制<br />\n唔再相信香港司法體制<br />\n咁香港再唔會被視為獨立經濟體<br />\n然後變成一個中國普通城市<br />\n外國企業即刻撤資<br />\n最後香港經濟收皮<br />\n以後工都唔駛返了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3c7159a45d040d6d4420e6246e0051cc25358f","tid":1385531,"uid":57737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:37:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5e69690fcc0c0e180d9d389e7cbdc225f96069b","tid":1385531,"uid":294582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26a9178e5511fbf2a18449ab1d069657558f5fdb","tid":1385531,"uid":71447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac